\section{Summary}

\begin{frame}
\frametitle{Key Concepts: Electric Charge}
\begin{block}{What We Discovered}
\begin{itemize}
\item Two types of charge: positive (protons) and negative (electrons)
\item Like charges repel, unlike charges attract
\item Fundamental unit: $e = 1.602 \times 10^{-19}$ C
\item Atoms are neutral (equal protons and electrons)
\end{itemize}
\end{block}
\note{- Review the four key ideas about charge\\\\
